track_notes: Starting from the Italian side of the montain, there is a long forest road first, then there is a good path to the summit where you will find a green pylone reflector.

As you must clim 1400m up, this track to the summit is for good walkers. Starting from the village Breil/Roya where you can park easily! Since the Alex storm in october 2020, the path may be destroyed; you must check that before you start. The place is fine and enought room on summit where is a pylone!
